Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(264,325)}E{\fsp-4}k{\fsp0}ē
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,俄羅斯製造的突擊步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那種也可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,圍棋社的話就是石頭了吧
